{
  "body" : "You are designing a single hero render of a brand logo concept.\n\nBRAND BRIEF\n- Brand name: {{brand_name}}\n- Industry / category: {{industry}}\n- Brand personality (3 adjectives): {{personality}}\n\nDESIGN DIRECTION\n- Logo style: {{style}}\n- Color palette: {{color_palette}}\n- Render presentation: {{presentation}}\n\nDESIGN RULES\n- Aspect: 4:5 portrait (~1024×1280) suitable for a brand-pitch deck slide\n- The logo is the ONLY hero — no other graphics competing\n- Brand name lettering must be crisply rendered, correctly spelled, and visually balanced\n- Mark + wordmark relationship clear; if mark only, keep it iconic\n- Style: identity-design portfolio polish — Pentagram, Collins, Mucho, &Walsh\n- Avoid: gradient mesh backgrounds, generic emblems, stock typefaces, drop shadows, AI-style chromatic aberrations, busy environments, mockup brand-guidelines layouts\n\nIf a field is empty, infer a default that aligns with the personality.",
  "cover" : {
    "dataBase64" : "",
    "format" : "png"
  },
  "folderName" : "Universal Briefs",
  "name" : "Universal · Logo Concept",
